@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

// =======================
// CONFLICT
// =======================

### POST crear conflicto (EJEMPLO)
POST {{baseUrl}}/conflicts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "War in Ukraine",
  "startDate": "2022-02-24",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "description": "Armed conflict between Ukraine and Russia."
}

### DELETE eliminar conflicto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/conflicts/1


